Yunzhou is young and inexperienced.

293
00:12:33,320 --> 00:12:35,399
You should know better.

294
00:12:36,399 --> 00:12:37,559
This cannot wait any longer.

295
00:12:37,840 --> 00:12:39,039
If we tolerate this today,

296
00:12:39,360 --> 00:12:41,000
our home will be in turmoil tomorrow.

297
00:12:41,879 --> 00:12:43,039
How will we protect our legacy?

298
00:12:43,759 --> 00:12:45,960
The Xiao Family's reputation must be protected.

299
00:12:46,720 --> 00:12:48,639
Expel these two from the estate

300
00:12:48,960 --> 00:12:49,960
to restore order.

301
00:12:50,240 --> 00:12:51,919
Since everyone feels this way,

302
00:12:52,519 --> 00:12:53,639
perhaps

303
00:12:54,559 --> 00:12:55,000
we...

304
00:12:55,000 --> 00:12:55,399
Reputation

305
00:12:56,399 --> 00:12:57,720
built on ignorance

306
00:12:58,360 --> 00:12:59,759
is but an empty shell.

307
00:13:00,559 --> 00:13:02,080
These two young ladies are injured.

308
00:13:02,080 --> 00:13:02,919
Expelling them

309
00:13:03,879 --> 00:13:05,720
would make me no better than a butcher.

310
00:13:07,000 --> 00:13:08,080
Rumors are already spreading.

311
00:13:09,000 --> 00:13:11,759
How will our clan face the world?

312
00:13:12,879 --> 00:13:15,320
I've heard the Su family's daughter

313
00:13:15,639 --> 00:13:16,720
abandoning her husband

314
00:13:17,000 --> 00:13:18,240
and violating moral norms.

315
00:13:18,320 --> 00:13:19,759
And Lin Yange,

316
00:13:19,919 --> 00:13:21,480
a renowned courtesan from the Bright Moon Pavilion,

317
00:13:22,200 --> 00:13:24,360
is tainted by scandal.

318
00:13:26,000 --> 00:13:27,279
Rumors stop with the wise.

319
00:13:27,720 --> 00:13:28,399
Good deeds

320
00:13:29,240 --> 00:13:30,679
should not cease because of gossip.

321
00:13:31,559 --> 00:13:33,159
The West Market Magistrate used his power for personal gain,

322
00:13:33,159 --> 00:13:34,039
enriching himself at the expense of the public.

323
00:13:34,039 --> 00:13:36,360
He is now being hunted by the entire city.

324
00:13:37,360 --> 00:13:38,559
Madam Su left her residence

325
00:13:39,320 --> 00:13:40,440
to clarify her intentions,

326
00:13:41,320 --> 00:13:42,519
not to abandon her husband.

327
00:13:43,799 --> 00:13:44,600
Lin Yange,

328
00:13:45,039 --> 00:13:46,159
though from the Bright Moon Pavilion

329
00:13:46,960 --> 00:13:47,840
and having endured hardships,

330
00:13:48,559 --> 00:13:48,960
is

331
00:13:49,200 --> 00:13:50,279
of noble character

332
00:13:50,840 --> 00:13:52,039
and is not actually diseased.

333
00:13:53,080 --> 00:13:54,679
She has even provided significant support

334
00:13:55,200 --> 00:13:56,519
to Madam Yin's clinic.

335
00:13:57,759 --> 00:13:58,559
The two young ladies

336
00:13:58,799 --> 00:13:59,759
are staying in the residence.

337
00:14:00,279 --> 00:14:00,919
Their behavior

338
00:14:01,759 --> 00:14:03,080
is in accordance with the rules.

339
00:14:04,360 --> 00:14:05,120
You're justifying their actions

340
00:14:05,120 --> 00:14:06,639
to protect them.

341
00:14:06,960 --> 00:14:08,000
Gossip can be damaging.

342
00:14:08,320 --> 00:14:09,080
If it becomes known

343
00:14:09,559 --> 00:14:10,639
that the Xiao family's eldest daughter

344
00:14:10,639 --> 00:14:12,720
associates with such women,

345
00:14:12,919 --> 00:14:14,159
we'll be the laughingstock.

346
00:14:15,799 --> 00:14:17,840
Yunzhou is young and kind-hearted.

347
00:14:18,360 --> 00:14:19,200
Please,

348
00:14:19,720 --> 00:14:21,559
don't be too harsh on him.

349
00:14:22,919 --> 00:14:23,960
Whether it's a laughingstock

350
00:14:24,720 --> 00:14:25,840
depends not on a woman's origins,

351
00:14:26,519 --> 00:14:28,039
but on a man's character.

352
00:14:28,759 --> 00:14:29,639
My father taught me

353
00:14:30,000 --> 00:14:31,159
to uphold virtue

354
00:14:31,559 --> 00:14:32,519
and not shirk from challenges,

355
00:14:32,960 --> 00:14:34,720
so I can uphold the family's honor.

356
00:14:35,720 --> 00:14:36,600
If you're here

357
00:14:37,000 --> 00:14:38,720
for the sake of reputation,

358
00:14:40,519 --> 00:14:41,759
then the Xiao Family's legacy

359
00:14:42,279 --> 00:14:43,639
is not worth me to uphold.

360
00:14:45,639 --> 00:14:45,960
Everyone,

361
00:14:47,159 --> 00:14:47,720
my apologies.

362
00:14:52,799 --> 00:14:53,360
Look!
